{"title":"Bookmark","content":"<h2><u><b>About MyAnimeList (MAL)  </b></u></h2>\n<p align=\"justify\">MyAnimeList (MAL) is the world’s largest anime and manga database and community. With syncing data to MAL database, you can create your personalized list from tens of thousands of titles on the world’s largest anime and manga database. You can use your list to organize and track what titles you’ve completed, your current progress, what you plan to watch or read and so much more. </p>\n<p align=\"justify\">By connecting with MAL, you can easily manage your bookmark in oxyanime.to, any other anime streaming platform that sync with MAL, MAL website or MAL App. MAL app is available on both iOS and Android platform.</p>\n<p>More info at: <a class=\"w3-text-blue\" href=\"https://myanimelist.net\" target=\"_blank\">https://myanimelist.net</a></p>\n<p>(Note: MAL is not our affiliated third party) </p>\n<h3><u>How to Connect with MyAnimeList (MAL) </u></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Click the “connect bookmark” icon on top of page. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DhNgRBZ.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>Click the green “connect” icon to connect to MyAnimeList. All bookmarked anime at here will be synced through MyAnimeList. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8e7AnVZ.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>If you already have MyAnimeList account, login your account to connect. If you do not have MyAnimeList account, sign up with any method you preferred shown in the list. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img  class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ESUsr0.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>Your will see the interface as below after login. (Or if you already have bookmarked before, it will show all your bookmarked anime) </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xafzfvz.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>To start bookmark, go to any anime you wish to bookmark then click the “Add Bookmark” icon.</li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sUZuiOi.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>Choose the type of bookmark you prefer and click update. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dqKp8D9.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>After bookmarked, you will see the bookmarked episode at anime streaming page as below. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bIgL70w.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>To check your bookmarked anime, click the green connect icon at top. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DZGm8wI.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>Then you will see all your bookmarked anime with MyAnimeList. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img  class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/38kCNRc.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>Click on any anime you have bookmarked, then you can choose action you preferred. </li>\n<ul>\n<li>Go Anime: Go to the anime.</li>\n<li>Edit: Update bookmark type, anime score, episode etc. </li>\n<li>Delete: Delete the anime from you bookmark. </li>\n<li>Cancel: Do nothing and back to bookmark page. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NZOXyH0.png\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<li>You may also add or update bookmark at anime streaming page by clicking the “Add Bookmark” or Episode icon below the player. </li>\n<div class=\"w3-row\">\n<img class=\"w3-threequarter\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hp1wzub.png\">\n</div>\n</ol>\n<br><br>\n<h5>Note: </h5>\n<p>If any of your bookmarked anime is not showing, it is probably due to MyAnimeList API data fetching issue. However, if it happens, feel free to contact us and we will do our best to solve the issue. </p>"}